<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title"><strong>ON THE AGENDA</strong> <span class="divider"> | </span></span> The Institute for Supply Management releases Augustâs   <b>manufacturing report</b>  at 10 a.m.  Data on  <b>construction spending in July</b>  will be released at 10 a.m.</p>
